comments: At the end of the drive, Dozier (DEN) firms up on his left foot and establishes himself in a legal guarding position when Durant (BKN) goes through him as he releases his pass.
Durant (BKN) and Barton (DEN) engage and disengage off-ball as Durant cuts to the perimeter to receive the pass.
Brown (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Murray (DEN).
LeVert (BKN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.

LeVert (BKN) moves into rebounding position and marginal contact occurs with Dozier's (DEN) side.  Dozier mistimes his jump on the putback attempt and the marginal contact does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Murray (DEN) jumps and extends his foot out to make contact with the ball.
Durant (BKN) and Barton (DEN) engage and disengage off-ball.
Barton (DEN) goes under Allen's (BKN) pick on the dribble hand off and immediately slides his hand off Allen's waist in one continuous motion.
Durant (BKN) plants his left foot and releases from the contact with Barton (DEN) on his step back jump shot attempt.
Murray (DEN) commits a take foul on Durant (BKN).
Barton (DEN) commits a take foul on Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN).
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Murray (DEN).
